  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a non-stick skillet or griddle over medium-high heat.",
    "Prepare the brioche buns by toasting them lightly on the inside and outside.",
    "Prepare the horseradish sauce by mixing it with mayonnaise and a squeeze of lemon juice.",
    "Season the cod fillet with salt and black pepper on both sides.",
    "Brush the cod fillet with olive oil and cook for 3-4 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "Meanwhile, toast the brioche buns on the griddle or in a toaster.",
    "Assemble the burger by spreading the horseradish sauce on the bottom bun, followed by a cod fillet, lettuce, tomato, red onion, pickles, and finally the top bun.",
    "Serve immediately and garnish with lemon wedges."
